&lt;p&gt;Syndio&#39;s partner ecosystem is a core growth driver, and the relationships we&#39;ve built with strategic partners require dedicated marketing investment to realize their full potential. We&#39;re hiring a Strategic Partner Marketing Manager to own the co-marketing function across our strategic partner portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;
