&lt;p&gt;This is a builder role. You&#39;ll extend existing partner programs and create new ones where nothing exists yet, working directly with senior stakeholders on both sides, and setting the standard for how Syndio approaches partner marketing at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our partner portfolio spans different categories of platforms — HR and workforce systems, communication and collaboration tools, and others — each with its own language, buyer, and marketplace dynamics. You&#39;ll need to adapt the value story and asset approach to fit each one.&lt;/p&gt;
